9-02T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d77d121bb0a7213c29a3088c2e6ab22deb197c","tid":1532064,"uid":15574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7061089bbe51e2f40068676d2f3f7443cffc035f","tid":1532064,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3282a87606e03bbcf28c929c1954008305844d19","tid":1532064,"uid":15574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱推入嚟推唔到要拍卡<br />\n推出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽朝繼續試<br />\n要補飛先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"雙手支撐，輕輕一跳，唔夠高就踩住跳，實得，識個矮撚都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"我151喎手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無我咁矮先"},{"pid":"f52f36a3d68a27b9b1954f37ca3eb106a5b0c9d5","tid":1532064,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1aotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=07f63dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"dac6be2f3ff390fb6eba8def3ff7960822a6917f","tid":1532064,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95d77d121bb0a7213c29a3088c2e6ab22deb197c","tid":1532064,"uid":15574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7061089bbe51e2f40068676d2f3f7443cffc035f","tid":1532064,"uid":114483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3282a87606e03bbcf28c929c1954008305844d19","tid":1532064,"uid":15574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"啱啱推入嚟推唔到要拍卡<br />\n推出就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽朝繼續試<br />\n要補飛先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"雙手支撐，輕輕一跳，唔夠高就踩住跳，實得，識個矮撚都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"我151喎手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無我咁矮先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"...."}]}